headline: Lamb Weston to Announce Fiscal Year 2025 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Financial Results on July 23, 2025
summary: EAGLE, Ind., July 02, 2025--Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) announced today it will report fiscal 2025 fourth quarter and full year financial results on July 23, 2025. The news release will be issued at approximately 8:00 a.m. ET, followed by a conference call at 10:00 a.m. ET.
